title: New York Times Bestseller Fiction Combined - 05-11-14
description:
The New York Times Best Seller list is widely considered the preeminent list of best-selling books in the United States. 

It is published weekly in The New York Times Book Review. The best-seller list has been ongoing since October 12, 1931.

Genre: Bestseller Collection, General Fiction, Romance, Mystery/Thriller
